rComments: While the discussions in class were highly engaging, the marking for tests was hard and the readings were difficult to understand. Papers were graded fairly with decent feedback. Test questions were fair and all based on the readings, some stuff based on discussion, but marking was overly difficult and we couldn't see what we did wrong after.
Really amazing prof. Cares a lot about his students. Friendly and approachable. He is there to help you when you need help. Fair grader and would recommend him to others.

He is the most adorable prof I've ever had. The pictures that he puts in his lecture slides can be so cute.  He is very approachable when it comes to course content and teaches very well. He is also very understanding of students, changing aspects of the course to cover more of what interested the class. It was a great course.
